iodic oscillation in the 2006\ndata, and we examine the outbursting behaviour of the system over a 4.5 year\nperiod.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Aug 2010 13:56:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Aug 2010 11:52:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
